28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150628233445/http://www.vancouversun.com/entertainment/movie-guide/Star+Trek+starts+filming+Vancouver+Squamish/11166551/story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Drew |first1=Brian |title=Star Trek Beyond Begins Production With Outdoor Shoot |url=http://trekmovie.com/2015/06/25/star-trek-beyond-begins-production-with-outdoor-shoot/ |accessdate=June 26, 2015 |work=trekmovie.com |date=June 25, 2015 |archive-date=2015-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150626220715/http://trekmovie.com/2015/06/25/star-trek-beyond-begins-production-with-outdoor-shoot/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。其他拍攝地點如[[韓國|韓國]]的[[首爾|首爾]]和[[阿拉伯聯合大公國|阿拉伯聯合大公國]]的[[杜拜|杜拜]]<ref>{{cite news |last1=Drew |first1=Brian |title=Mayor: Portion Of Star Trek 2016 To Be Shot In Seoul, S. Korea |url=http://trekmovie.com/2014/09/30/mayor-of-seoul-met-star-trek-2016-team-to-talk-about-filming-in-korea/ |accessdate=October 7, 2014 |publisher=trekmovie.com |date=September 30, 2014 |archive-date=2014-10-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141007092037/http://trekmovie.com/2014/09/30/mayor-of-seoul-met-star-trek-2016-team-to-talk-about-filming-in-korea/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Newbould |first1=Chris |title=Producers confirm Star Trek Beyond will be filmed in Dubai |url=http://www.thenational.ae/arts-lifestyle/film/producers-confirm-star-trek-beyond-will-be-filmed-in-dubai |accessdate=July 2, 2015 |work=thenational.ae |date=July 2, 2015 |archive-date=2015-07-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150703231332/http://www.thenational.ae/arts-lifestyle/film/producers-confirm-star-trek-beyond-will-be-filmed-in-dubai |dead-url=no }}</ref>。主要拍攝於2015年10月15日結束。2016年3月，因為[[索瑞·安達斯魯|索瑞·安達斯魯]]的加入而又重拍了部分片段<ref name="Deadline">{{cite news |url=http://deadline.com/2016/03/shohreh-aghdashloo-star-trek-beyond-paramount-1201718696/ |title=Shohreh Aghdashloo Has Boarded ‘Star Trek Beyond’ |work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] |last=Busch |first=Anita |date=March 11, 2016 |accessdate=2016-11-29 |archive-date=2016-03-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160312064102/http://deadline.com/2016/03/shohreh-aghdashloo-star-trek-beyond-paramount-1201718696/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 發行 ==
2015年12月，該片原本定於2016年7月8日在[[美國|美國]]上映<ref name=Release>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/12/23/star-trek-3-release-date-set-for-july-2016|title=Star Trek 3 Release Date Set For July 2016|publisher=IGN|last=Moser|first=Cassidee|date=December 23, 2014|accessdate=2016-11-29|archive-date=2015-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150720193211/http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/12/23/star-trek-3-release-date-set-for-july-2016|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年9月，上映日延期至2016年7月22日<ref>{{cite news|last1=McNary|first1=Dave|title=‘Star Trek: Beyond’ Gets New Release Date|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/star-trek-beyond-gets-new-release-date-1201596328/|accessdate=September 18, 2015|work=variety.com|date=September 17, 2015|archive-date=2015-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150920005040/http://variety.com/2015/film/news/star-trek-beyond-gets-new-release-date-1201596328/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 市場營銷 ===
2015年12月14日，釋出首支預告<ref>{{cite web|first=Sandy|last=Schaefer|date=December 14, 2015|url=http://screenrant.com/star-trek-beyond-trailer-2016/|title=Star Trek Beyond Teaser Trailer: Find Hope in the Impossible.|work=ScreenRant.com|accessdate=January 9, 2016|archive-date=2016-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160112153211/http://screenrant.com/star-trek-beyond-trailer-2016/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。但該預告受到了粉絲的批評，主要認為預告過於集中在動作要素，且搭配[[野獸男孩|野獸男孩]]的歌曲《Sabotage》使人出戲。這就連[[賽門·佩吉|賽門·佩吉]]也表示不太滿意，但認為這是要表達電影充滿了動作和樂趣<ref>Barnes, Henry (December 18, 2015).  [http://www.theguardian.com/film/2015/dec/18/simon-pegg-critical-of-star-trek-beyond-trailer-justin-lin "Simon Pegg Joins Criticism of Star Trek Beyond Trailer."] {{Wayback|url=http://www.theguardian.com/film/2015/dec/18/simon-pegg-critical-of-star-trek-beyond-trailer-justin-lin |date=20201112013730 }}  ''TheGuardian.com''.  Retrieved January 9, 2016.</ref>。第二支預告於2016年5月20日釋出，這才獲得了粉絲較佳的反應。最終版預告片於2016年6月27日釋出，其中包含了[[蕾哈娜|蕾哈娜]]的新單曲《Sledgehammer》。

