== 迴響 ==
=== 評價 ===
在[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]上，基於295條評論獲得了85%的新鮮度，平均得分7/10<ref name="RT">{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/star_trek_beyond/ |title=Star Trek Beyond (2016) |website=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |accessdate=July 15, 2016 |archive-date=2018-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181008043116/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/star_trek_beyond/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分68<ref name="Meta">{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/star-trek-beyond |title=Star Trek Beyond reviews |website=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |accessdate=July 15, 2016 |archive-date=2016-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160716153220/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/star-trek-beyond |dead-url=no }}</ref>。據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，觀眾的平均評價於A+至F間落於「A-」<ref name="CinemaScore">{{cite web |url=https://m.cinemascore.com |title=CinemaScore |work=cinemascore.com |accessdate=2020-10-12 |archive-date=2019-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191210223808/https://m.cinemascore.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。普遍認為其水準不輸前兩集，大多稱讚電影史詩科幻的娛樂感、懸疑與動作。

=== 票房 ===
在美國和加拿大，早期預估在首映週末票房為5000萬至6000萬美元，可能會與前兩集相差不遠<ref name="DEADproj">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/07/star-trek-beyond-box-office-projection-ghostbusters-secret-life-of-pets-1201782223/|title=‘Star Trek Beyond’ Could Hit $60M Opening, According To Some Early Projections|author=Anthony D'Alessandro|work=''[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]''|date=July 1, 2016|accessdate=July 2, 2016|archive-date=2016-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160702143748/https://deadline.com/2016/07/star-trek-beyond-box-office-projection-ghostbusters-secret-life-of-pets-1201782223/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在國際上，該片有望能獲得良好表現，如俄羅斯、韓國、中國和拉丁美洲市場。美國首映週末票房為5960萬美元，成績為該系列第三高，但卻比前兩集重啟電影低<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2016/07/24/star-trek-beyond-box-office-when-a-59-million-weekend-is-just-okay/|title='Star Trek Beyond' Box Office: When A $59 Million Weekend Is Just 'Okay'|author=Scott Mendelson|work=[[Forbes|Forbes]]|date=July 24, 2016|accessdate=July 24, 2016|archive-date=2020-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204143030/https://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2016/07/24/star-trek-beyond-box-office-when-a-59-million-weekend-is-just-okay/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。被認為是因為該片在美國的宣傳不多，且片商未能在五十周年紀念好好行銷所致。

儘管北美票房表現普通，但在中國大陸取得4.4亿人民币。全球票房最終總計3.43億美元。

