//torontosun.com/2016/07/14/jj-abrams-star-trek-wont-replace-anton-yelchin|title=J.J. Abrams: 'Star Trek' won't replace Anton Yelchin|publisher=Toronto Sun|last=Slotek|first=Jim|date=July 13, 2016|accessdate=2016-07-25|archive-date=2016-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160716122852/http://www.torontosun.com/2016/07/14/jj-abrams-star-trek-wont-replace-anton-yelchin|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

